{"_path":"/trail/t006","_dir":"trail","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"楓樹坑步道 / 龜崙山","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":6,"category":"龜山","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-30T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"楓樹坑步道-龜崙山"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"楓樹坑步道 / 龜崙山"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"步道簡介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"步道簡介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"楓樹坑登山步道是桃園虎頭山眾多登山步道之一，登山入口就位於楓樹村光峰路 281 巷的巷底，由此進入後，會先經過楓樹國小的側門，再由福德宮旁的車道續往上行，即可抵達主祀玄天上帝的真武殿，殿內環境清幽，也是一處參訪的好地點，廟旁有條筆直的枕木階梯就是楓樹坑登山步道的起點。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"自行開車"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自行開車"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由華亞三鹿，經振興路。與縱貫路交會時, 右轉長壽路/台 1 線。遇光峰路右轉 於光峰路 281 巷進入就達豋山口．\n停車位：在光峰路上有少數路邊停車位。平日有空位機會"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"公共運輸"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公共運輸"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由長庚醫院站 搭乘 5063 / 5116 公車經 21 個站 約 39 分鐘到楓樹社區（楓樹國小）下車。 再由光峰路 281 巷進入，步行 4 分鐘即可達。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"相關介紹"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相關介紹"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健行筆記 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://hiking.biji.co/index.php?q=trail&act=detail&id=1239"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"楓樹坑步道(龜崙山)"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Youtube 2020/11/13 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=igImMaliLWQ"},"children":[{"type"